@node "INFO" "SN User-o-Meter v1.3 - Information"
@toc "MAIN"
┌────────────────────────────────────┐
  SN User-o-Meter v1.3 - Information
└────────────────────────────────────┘

   Ever need to see which users are the most active and valuable to
your system?  How about your users?  Are they curious, too?  Well,
here's the solution!  This program is very simple to install and
even easier to maintain!  Just follow the installation instructions
and watch it go!

Features to note:
  - Multi-line compatible.  You don't have to worry about conflictions.
  - Self-cleaning.  Leaves no temp files lying around.
  - First use automatically creates all needed files.
  - Very nice ANSI menuing routines.
  - Path self-aware.  No matter where you put it, it'll work.
  - No configs to hand-modify - everything done ONLINE!
  - A very comprehensive and informative (even to the SysOp) online
    help system.
  - Allows you and your users to see their own stats, another's or
    one of the following lists:

      Ranked  - A sorted list of every user in order from highest
                to lowest points
      Ordered - An unsorted list of every user in order of account
                numbers
      TopTen  - A sorted list of the top ten active users

  - The Tools Menu provides a way to find out various information,
    sort/view/select by criteria.  You have to see this one!
  - ALAS (Automated Level Adjustment System) provides an easy and
    fully automated way for you to raise or lower users' access
    levels based on their activity.  Or, she can only "suggest"
    changes and you make the final decision.  Either way, this is
    a major time-saving device!

  Note:  The Tools Menu and ALAS are only including in the registered
         version.  The registered version is a whopping 12k larger and
         seems to be growing.  :)  Screen shots are included to whet
         your appetite.

───SN/AHI (910) 326-3804 (28.8k)─────────────────────────────────────────
@endnode
@node "HISTORY" "SN User-o-Meter v1.3 - History"
@toc "MAIN"
┌────────────────────────────────┐
  SN User-o-Meter v1.3 - History
└────────────────────────────────┘

  v1.3 - Configuration is now handled completely online.  Tools has been
         improved but now only supports ANSI terminals (it was getting too
         hard to support both).
  v1.2 - Now uses more ANSI menus.  Improved the configuration routines.
         New menu (selectable access):  Tools.  Improved the online
         help system.
  v1.1 - Added path self-awareness.  Moved the configuration from the
         program itself to a configuration file.  All variables editable
         online.  New SysOp menu including:  Edit Config, Update.
  v1.0 - First release.  ALAS routines still under construction
         and are not included in this package.

───SN/AHI (910) 326-3804 (28.8k)─────────────────────────────────────────
@endnode
